[SN]TITLE[SN]
Hull schoolgirl Alishia Swain 'breaks gloves world record'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The world record for the most gloves put on one hand in 60 seconds has been unofficially broken by a schoolgirl in Hull.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
9 July 2015 Last updated at 13:08 BST
Winifred Holtby Academy said student Alishia Swain managed to put on 22 gloves in one minute. That beats a 2011 record of 13, but is awaiting validation.
